Localization.Name: Alban Shirt Striker
Localization.Description: The Alban is a long sleeve shirt made from comfortable, natural fabrics. Featuring a deep V-neck, its asymmetrical patchwork design provides it with a bit of texture and a two-toned look.\n\nThe Striker edition is a worn grey with dark grey patches.

stdItem.DescriptionText:
The Alban is a long sleeve shirt made from comfortable, natural fabrics. Featuring a deep V-neck, its asymmetrical patchwork design provides it with a bit of texture and a two-toned look.

The Striker edition is a worn grey with dark grey patches.
